OL,7,FTraders, tenants, and residents at
OL,8,FHeartlands say they are concerned
OL,9,Fabout their futures
OL,11,FIt comes after the National Lottery
OL,12,Fpulled its funding saying the visitor
OL,13,Fattraction was unsustainable.
OL,15,FHeartlands opened 12 years ago and
OL,16,Freinvigorated Cornwall's heart of
OL,17,Fmining as a celebration of its
OL,18,Findustrial heritage.
