OL,4,Cvisitor attraction say they've been
OL,5,Cforgotten
OL,7,FNow, everything run by its charitable
OL,8,Ftrust is closed, leaving those still
OL,9,Ftrading and living on the site in Pool
OL,10,Fwondering if Heartlands will become a
OL,11,Fwasteland.
OL,13,FThe museum, Red River Cafe, Wheal Play
OL,14,Fsoft play centre and conference centre
OL,15,Fhave all permanently shut up shop.
OL,17,FThe chairman of the trust said that
OL,18,Fthe council has not given commercial
OL,19,Fand residential tenants any details of
OL,20,Fcontacts for maintenance and security.
