OL,7,FJacky said: "A senior member of
OL,8,FCornwall Council has reached out to us
OL,9,Fwith regard to our collective and
OL,10,Findividual needs as commercial units,
OL,11,Fbut as yet we have no contact
OL,12,Finformation with regard to
OL,13,Femergencies, ongoing studio
OL,14,Fmaintenance or site security.
OL,16,F"Anti-social behaviour will become an
OL,17,Fissue if the site is left derelict. In
OL,18,Ffact, it's already started happening.
