OL,7,F"There are a lot of stones across the
OL,8,Fsite which are being thrown in the
OL,9,Fwater containers and a window had been
OL,10,Fsmashed this morning.
OL,12,F"Things have started going missing
OL,13,Ftoo, including a picnic bench."
OL,15,FJacky said she has heard passers-by
OL,16,Fsaying the retail units will close as
OL,17,Fwell. "We want to assure members of
OL,18,Fthe public that the businesses here
OL,19,Fare still trading as usual," she
OL,20,Fstressed.
