OL,7,F"I've watched 27 businesses go from
OL,8,Fthis part of the site in the 11 years
OL,9,FI have been here; creative enterprises
OL,10,Fthat members of the public ` even in
OL,11,Fthe locale ` were not aware existed.
OL,13,F"Poor marketing, a lack of curiosity
OL,14,Ffrom the wider public and an appalling
OL,15,Flack of signage on site has all
OL,16,Fcontributed to the lack of footfall.
