OL,7,F"Add to that ticketing of events so
OL,8,Fthat access to the commercial units
OL,9,Fwas limited or non-existent and that
OL,10,Fwas the kiss of death for many of the
OL,11,Fcreatives here.
OL,13,F"My own future hangs in the balance
OL,14,F... I don't see that we can 'mothball'
OL,15,Fa site that cost in excess of #30
OL,16,Fmillion to create.
OL,18,F"I'm hoping from the ashes something
OL,19,Fgood will rise."
