OL,7,FDavid Collins has been living in his
OL,8,Fflat for 18 months. In an ideal
OL,9,Fposition, the living room overlooks
OL,10,Fthe once bustling open courtyard
OL,11,Ffeaturing the dramatic engine house.
OL,12,FIt's now completely dead. "If you want
OL,13,Fto live somewhere peaceful and
OL,14,Ftranquil, there's nowhere better," he
OL,15,Fjoked.
