OL,7,F"I asked the staff what the council
OL,8,Fhad told them about the future of the
OL,9,Fsite and the properties. Nothing.
OL,10,FWe've heard nothing from the council.
OL,11,FYour guess is as good as mine. It's
OL,12,Fdisgusting."
OL,14,FDavid added: "We pay service charges
OL,15,Fand everything to Heartlands. Who do
OL,16,Fwe pay now? This is our council and
OL,17,Ftheir property. The least they can do
OL,18,Fis keep us in the loop.
