OL,7,F"I had a nice little bungalow in
OL,8,FTolgus, but wanted to move somewhere
OL,9,Fsmaller after my wife died.
OL,11,F"I thought this place would be ideal `
OL,12,Fthere was a thriving cafe and it was
OL,13,Freally popular. To face this now is
OL,14,Fdemoralising."
OL,16,FLike others, he fears vandalism saying
OL,17,Fthere were staff employed to oversee
OL,18,Fsecurity, but doesn't know what will
OL,19,Fhappen now.
