OL,4,Cvisitor attraction say they've been
OL,5,Cforgotten
OL,7,FSpeaking on Tuesday 30 January
OL,8,Ffollowing a meeting between the
OL,9,FHeartlands Trust and Cornwall Council,
OL,10,Fthe trust's chairman David Sillifant
OL,11,Fsaid: "Unfortunately the meeting
OL,12,Fchanged very little.
OL,14,FThe trust will cease trading tomorrow
OL,15,Fand it will be the end of employment
OL,16,Ffor our staff. It is terribly sad `
OL,17,Fthe Lottery will not allow any further
OL,18,Faccess to our endowment to keep anyone
OL,19,Fon, even for a managed wind down. You
OL,20,Fcan imagine how devastated the staff
OL,21,Fare.
