OL,7,FA spokesperson for the local authority
OL,8,Fsaid: "The council is committed to
OL,9,Fmaintaining public access to the parks
OL,10,Fand gardens at Heartlands, once the
OL,11,Ftrust's legal obligations under the
OL,12,Flease and management agreement come to
OL,13,Fan end.
OL,15,F"The council will carry out an
OL,16,Fassessment and if necessary undertake
OL,17,Fworks so that they can safely remain
OL,18,Fopen. The registration service and
OL,19,Fcommercially let shops and offices
OL,20,Fremain open."
